  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">La Alegria de los Ninos is a shelter home for children from 0 to 6 years old rescued from violence or abandonment, that lived in dysfunctional environments and that require a safe place where they can be healed physically and emotionally. Our current project is oriented to strengthen our medical program and provide integral medical attention to the children in our Institution, in order to recover, maintain or control their health. THE RIGHT TO A GOOD HEALTH IS A FUNDAMENTAL RIGHT.</narrative>
  </description>
